dct_description_sm: This line data layer represents interstates, US highways, and Minnesota highways for Minnesota in 2006. The dataset was originally published by the Minnesota Department of Transportation in 2007.[Route_Segment_History represents road centerlines for all public roads within the state of Minnesota. The roads are broken from intersection to intersection and attributed with information based on their designated route. A description of the Roads layer is included in Section 5 of this document - Entity and Attribute Overview.]
